ds/2024/12/Shaboozey-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Shaboozey-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Shaboozey-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Shaboozey">Shaboozey</a>以其歌曲“A Bar Song (Tipsy)”成为最新加入<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/spotify">Spotify</a>亿万俱乐部的音乐家。</p><p>这位美国歌手兼制作人在他的 Instagram 官方账户上分享了这一荣誉，并附上了一张自己穿着白色服装、戴着白色毛皮帽子的照片，这与他在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-beyonce-debut-cowboy-carter-setlist-for-hometown-christmas-day-halftime-show-3824799">圣诞节中场秀</a>中与<a href="/artists/Beyonce">碧昂丝</a>一起表演时所穿的装束很相似。 Instagram 故事。</p><p> “同一天有十亿条流 + 碧昂丝碗。这是一个圣诞节奇迹，”他在帖子的标题中写道。他还分享了一张来自 Spotify 的数十亿俱乐部照片，并附有标题：“有史以来最好的圣诞礼物@spotify”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3824999" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3824999" style="width: 1500px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3824999" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Shaboozey.-Credit-screengrab-from-Shaboozeys-Instagram.jpg" alt="沙布泽。图片来源：Shaboozey 的 Instagram 屏幕截图" width="1500" height="2716" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Shaboozey.-Credit-screengrab-from-Shaboozeys-Instagram.jpg 1500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Shaboozey.-Credit-screengrab-from-Shaboozeys-Instagram-400x724.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Shaboozey.-Credit-screengrab-from-Shaboozeys-Instagram-800x1449.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Shaboozey.-Credit-screengrab-from-Shaboozeys-Instagram-696x1260.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Shaboozey.-Credit-screengrab-from-Shaboozeys-Instagram-1392x2520.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Shaboozey.-Credit-screengrab-from-Shaboozeys-Instagram-1068x1934.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3824999" class="wp-caption-text">沙布泽。图片来源：Shaboozey 的 Instagram 屏幕截图</figcaption></figure><p>《A Bar Song (Tipsy)》目前与 Gabby Barrett 的热门歌曲《I Hope》并列，后者在 2020 年登上排行榜榜首，成为本十年美国告示牌热门乡村歌曲排行榜上最长的第一名，总共 27 首图表顶部的周数。</p><p>据 Luminate 统计，自 5 月份以来，Shaboozey 的热门歌曲已播放了 1750 万次，播放次数达到了 6380 万次。早在 11 月，这首歌曲就与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-nas-x">Lil Nas X</a>的《Old Town Road》并列占据 Billboard Hot 100 排行榜榜首的多数周时间，此前该歌曲总共占据了第一名 19 周。 </p><figure id="attachment_3825000" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3825000" style="width: 1500px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3825000" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/shaboozey-IG-Story.-Credit-screengrab-of-Sahbooxeys-Instagram-stories.jpg" alt="Shaboozey IG 故事。图片来源：Sahbooxey 的 Instagram 故事的屏幕截图" width="1500" height="2700" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/shaboozey-IG-Story.-Credit-screengrab-of-Sahbooxeys-Instagram-stories.jpg 1500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/shaboozey-IG-Story.-Credit-screengrab-of-Sahbooxeys-Instagram-stories-400x720.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/shaboozey-IG-Story.-Credit-screengrab-of-Sahbooxeys-Instagram-stories-800x1440.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/shaboozey-IG-Story.-Credit-screengrab-of-Sahbooxeys-Instagram-stories-696x1253.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/shaboozey-IG-Story.-Credit-screengrab-of-Sahbooxeys-Instagram-stories-1392x2506.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/shaboozey-IG-Story.-Credit-screengrab-of-Sahbooxeys-Instagram-stories-1068x1922.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3825000" class="wp-caption-text"> Shaboozey IG 故事。图片来源：Shaboozey 的 Instagram 故事的屏幕截图</figcaption></figure><p>《A Bar Song (Tipsy)》被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">提名为第 67 届格莱美奖年度歌曲、最佳乡村歌曲和最佳乡村独奏表演奖</a>，该颁奖典礼将于 2025 年 2 月 2 日在洛杉矶 Crypto.com Arena 举行，加利福尼亚州。沙布泽本人也获得了最佳新人奖提名。</p><p>周三（12 月 25 日），沙布西与碧昂斯一起出现在她的家乡德克萨斯州休斯顿，为 NFL 圣诞节比赛中场秀做主角。在那里，两人表演了“Spaghettii/Riiverdance/Sweet Honey Buckiin”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DEBdz6-OykG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.